data.name: grdMaster.QuerySQL
data.value: SELECT DISTINCT A.RESER_DATE ODER_DATE ,B.BUNHO BUNHO ,FN_OUT_LOAD_SUNAME(B.BUNHO, B.HOSP_CODE) SUNAME ,A.DRG_BUNHO DRG_BUNHO ,B.DOCTOR DOCTOR ,FN_BAS_LOAD_DOCTOR_NAME(B.DOCTOR, B.ORDER_DATE, B.HOSP_CODE) DOCTOR_NAME ,DECODE(A.DRG_BUNHO, NULL, 'N', 'Y') PRINT_YN ,A.JUBSU_DATE JUBSU_DATE ,D.GWA ,D.NAEWON_TYPE ,D.ORDER_DATE FROM OCS0103 E ,OCS1003 D ,INV0110 C ,INJ1001 B ,INJ1002 A WHERE A.RESER_DATE BETWEEN :f_from_date AND :f_to_date AND A.HOSP_CODE = :f_hosp_code AND B.PKINJ1001 = A.FKINJ1001 AND B.BUNHO LIKE NVL(:f_bunho,'%') AND A.HANGMOG_CODE = E.HANGMOG_CODE AND C.JAERYO_CODE = E.JAERYO_CODE AND D.PKOCS1003 = B.FKOCS1003 AND (NVL(C.CHK7,'N') = 'Y' OR NVL(C.CHKB,'N') = 'Y') AND :f_anti_yn = 'N' AND A.HOSP_CODE = B.HOSP_CODE AND A.HOSP_CODE = C.HOSP_CODE AND A.HOSP_CODE = D.HOSP_CODE AND A.HOSP_CODE = E.HOSP_CODE UNION SELECT DISTINCT A.RESER_DATE ODER_DATE ,B.BUNHO BUNHO ,FN_OUT_LOAD_SUNAME(B.BUNHO, B.HOSP_CODE) SUNAME ,A.DRG_BUNHO DRG_BUNHO ,B.DOCTOR DOCTOR ,FN_BAS_LOAD_DOCTOR_NAME(B.DOCTOR, B.ORDER_DATE, B.HOSP_CODE) DOCTOR_NAME ,DECODE(A.DRG_BUNHO, NULL, 'N', 'Y') PRINT_YN ,A.JUBSU_DATE JUBSU_DATE ,D.GWA ,D.NAEWON_TYPE ,D.ORDER_DATE FROM OCS0103 E ,OCS1003 D ,INV0110 C ,INJ1001 B ,INJ1002 A WHERE A.RESER_DATE BETWEEN :f_from_date AND :f_to_date AND A.HOSP_CODE = :f_hosp_code AND B.PKINJ1001 = A.FKINJ1001 AND B.BUNHO LIKE NVL(:f_bunho,'%') AND A.HANGMOG_CODE = E.HANGMOG_CODE AND C.JAERYO_CODE = E.JAERYO_CODE AND D.PKOCS1003 = B.FKOCS1003 AND NVL(C.CHKB,'N') = 'Y' AND :f_anti_yn = 'Y' AND A.HOSP_CODE = B.HOSP_CODE AND A.HOSP_CODE = C.HOSP_CODE AND A.HOSP_CODE = D.HOSP_CODE AND A.HOSP_CODE = E.HOSP_CODE ORDER BY 7, 1, 4, 5

data.value: SELECT A.MIX_GROUP MIX_GROUP, C.HANGMOG_NAME HANGMOG_NAME, G.CODE_NAME TONGGYE_CODE, A.HANGMOG_CODE HANGMOG_CODE, TO_CHAR(E.ORDER_DATE, 'YYYY/MM/DD') ORDER_DATE , FN_OCS_LOAD_CODE_NAME('ORD_DANUI', F.ORD_DANUI, F.HOSP_CODE) DANUI_NAME , F.BOGYONG_CODE BOGYONG_CODE, F.SURYANG SURYANG, F.DV DV, DECODE(F.DV_TIME, '#', '/', F.DV_TIME) DV_TIME, FN_OCS_LOAD_CODE_NAME('JUSA_SPD_GUBUN', F.JUSA_SPD_GUBUN, F.HOSP_CODE) JUSA_SPD_GUBUN, A.GROUP_SER GROUP_SER, F.INPUT_GUBUN INPUT_GUBUN, F.HOPE_DATE HOPE_DATE FROM OCS0132 G, OCS1003 F, INJ1001 E, INV0110 D, OCS0103 C, INJ0102 B, INJ1002 A WHERE A.RESER_DATE = :f_reser_date AND A.HOSP_CODE = :f_hosp_code AND NVL(A.DRG_BUNHO,0) = NVL(:f_drg_bunho,0) AND B.CODE (+)= A.TONGGYE_CODE AND B.CODE_TYPE (+)= '03' AND B.HOSP_CODE (+)= A.HOSP_CODE AND C.HANGMOG_CODE = A.HANGMOG_CODE AND C.HOSP_CODE = A.HOSP_CODE AND D.JAERYO_CODE = C.JAERYO_CODE AND D.HOSP_CODE = C.HOSP_CODE AND E.PKINJ1001 = A.FKINJ1001 AND E.BUNHO = :f_bunho AND E.NALSU > 0 AND E.HOSP_CODE = A.HOSP_CODE AND F.PKOCS1003 = E.FKOCS1003 AND NVL(F.WONYOI_ORDER_YN,'N') != 'Y' AND F.HOSP_CODE = E.HOSP_CODE AND G.CODE_TYPE (+)= 'JUSA' AND G.CODE (+)= A.TONGGYE_CODE AND G.HOSP_CODE (+)= A.HOSP_CODE ORDER BY A.RESER_DATE , A.GROUP_SER, A.MIX_GROUP , A.SEQ ASC
